@NODE "Introduction" "Introduction"

 @{FG SHINE}@{U}Introduction@{UU}:@{FG TEXT}

   ThumbNail is a small proggie that uses GfxCon for the ThumbNail making
   and it also makes a HTML file for all the pics. It has many nice features:
   @{B}*@{UB} MUI interface. (Using MUIRexx!)
   @{B}*@{UB} It's small.
   @{B}*@{UB} It's very easy to use.
@ENDNODE

@NODE "Disclaimer" "Disclaimer"

 @{FG SHINE}@{U}Disclaimer@{UU}:@{FG TEXT}

   You are using this program at your own risk. I'm NOT responsible for
   anything this program might do. (@{B}Although it shouldn't do any damage!@{UB})
@ENDNODE

@NODE "Copyright" "Copyright"

 @{FG SHINE}@{U}Copyright@{UU}:@{FG TEXT}

   ThumbNail is ©Copyright Lorens Johansson 1998.
   This program is E-Mailware... If you use it then please send me an E-Mail
   so I can see how many people who uses this program... That's all I ask.
@ENDNODE

@NODE "Requirements" "Requirements"

 @{FG SHINE}@{U}Requirements@{UU}:@{FG TEXT}

   · AmigaOS 2.0+ (Since ARexx was introduced in 2.0)
   · You must have GFXCon.
   · The following libraries in LIBS:
     rexxarplib.library
     rexxdossupport.library
     rexxkuang11.library 0.26+
     rexxsupport.library
     openurl.library 2.0+ (for the browser start button).
   · You must have MUIRexx installed and a MUIRexx assign to it.
@ENDNODE

@NODE "Install" "How to install"

 @{FG SHINE}@{U}How to install@{UU}:@{FG TEXT}

   Copy the program and the guide file to wherever you want.
   Copy the following libraries to LIBS:
   - rexxarplib.library
   - rexxdossupport.library
   - rexxkuang11.library
   - rexxsupport.library
   - openurl.library (if you wanna be able to use the Start Browser button!)
   Be sure that you have MUIRexx: assigned to where MUIRexx is.
   That's it!
@ENDNODE

@NODE "HowTo" "How to use"

 @{FG SHINE}@{U}How to use@{UU}:@{FG TEXT}

   Please E-Mail me if you have any trouble with this program, and I'll
   do my best to help you!

@{FG SHINE}____________________________________________________________________________@{FG TEXT}
ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ
                              T H E   M E N U
@{FG SHINE}____________________________________________________________________________@{FG TEXT}
ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ
    @{B}@{U}* ThumbNailMaker@{UU}@{UB}
      @{B}About MUI:@{UB}
         Shows the About MUI requester.
      @{B}About:@{UB}
         Shows some info about the program.
      @{B}Quit:@{UB}
         Quits the program.
    @{B}@{U}* Settings@{UU}@{UB}
      @{B}Save Settings...@{UB}
         Saves the settings.
      @{B}MUI Prefs...@{UB}
         Brings up the MUI preferences...
@{FG SHINE}____________________________________________________________________________@{FG TEXT}
ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ
                               T H E   G U I
@{FG SHINE}____________________________________________________________________________@{FG TEXT}
ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ
    @{B}@{U}* Main Settings:@{UB}@{UU}
      @{B}@{U}* GFXCon Settings:@{UB}@{UU}
        @{B}* GfxCON:@{UB}
          The path to GfxCON, including the executeable file.
        @{B}* ThumbNail size X:@{UB}
          The horizontal size of the ThumbNails!
        @{B}* ThumbNail size Y:@{UB}
          The vertical size of the ThumbNails!
        @{B}* JPEG Quality:@{UB}
          The quality of the thumbnails. (Only affects JPEG pictures!)
        @{B}* ThumbNail format:@{UB}
          Which format the ThumbNails should be! For example gif or jpg.

      @{B}@{U}* General Settings:@{UB}@{UU}
        @{B}* Filepattern:@{UB}
          Which files the program should ignore! This is a normal dos pattern.
        @{B}* Source directory:@{UB}
          The directory where the pictures are!
        @{B}* ThumbNail dest dir:@{UB}
          The name of the subdirectory where the ThumbNails should be stored,
          ONLY a name no path or slash.
        @{B}* Quiet:@{UB}
          Puts >NIL: in the commandline! ie, GFXCon won't show the errors in a
          separate window!

    @{B}@{U}* HTML Settings:@{UB}@{UU}
      @{B}* HTML names:@{UB}
        Choose what the indexfilenames should be! (xxxxxx1.html)
      @{B}* Pics per page:@{UB}
        How many ThumbNails each index page should have.
      @{B}* X Resolution:@{UB}
        Which horizontal resolution the page should be optimized for!
      @{B}* Table border:@{UB}
        How thick the border of the table should be!
      @{B}* Header:@{UB}
        What text it would be in the header of the index HTML files!
        You can use HTML tags too.
        Press the popupbutton and check what templates that exists, then just
        type them wherever you want them!
      @{B}* Footer:@{UB}
        What text it would be in the footer of the index HTML files!
        You can use HTML tags too.
        Press the popupbutton and check what templates that exists, then just
        type them wherever you want them!
      @{B}@{U}* Indexlinks:@{UB}@{UU}
        @{B}* Where:@{UB}
          Choose where to put the links between the indexpages.
        @{B}* FontSize:@{UB}
          Choose the fontsize of the Index links.
      @{B}@{U}* Stuff under ThumbNail:@{UB}@{UU}
        @{B}* Font size:@{UB}
          Choose what size the text under the pictures should have.
        @{B}* Add LineFeed:@{UB}
          Choose if you want an empty line between the picture and the
          filename/size.
        @{B}* Add Filename:@{UB}
          Check this if you want to put the filename under the picture!
        @{B}* Add Filesize:@{UB}
          Check this if you want to put the size under the picture, and choose
          from Bytes or KiloBytes

    @{B}@{U}* HTML Pic Settings:@{UB}@{UU}
      @{B}* Make HTML pages for pictures:@{UB}
        Check this if the pictures should have an HTML page!
      @{B}* Header:@{UB}
        What text it would be in the header of the picture HTML files!
        You can use HTML tags too.
      @{B}* Footer:@{UB}
        What text it would be in the footer of the picture HTML files!
        You can use HTML tags too.

    @{B}@{U}* HTML Colours:@{UB}@{UU}
      @{U}* Background:@{UU}
        @{B}* BGColour:@{UB}
          Which colour the HTML files BGs should use!
        @{B}* BGPicture:@{UB}
          Which picture the HTML files BGs should use!
      @{U}* Colours:@{UU}
        @{B}* Text Colour:@{UB}
          Which color the Texts should have! (Like #0000FF)
        @{B}* Link Colour:@{UB}
          Which color the Links should have! (Like #0000FF)
        @{B}* ALink Colour:@{UB}
          Which color the ALinks should have! (Like #0000FF)
        @{B}* VLink Colour:@{UB}
          Which color the Visited Links should have! (Like #0000FF)

@{FG SHINE}____________________________________________________________________________@{FG TEXT}
ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ
                               B U T T O N S
@{FG SHINE}____________________________________________________________________________@{FG TEXT}
ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ
    @{B}* Start@{UB}
      Starts making thumbnails and HTML pages if chosen!
    @{B}* Browser@{UB}
      Uses OpenURL.library to start a browser and loads the firt index page!
    @{B}* About@{UB}
      This button shows some info about ThumbNailMaker.
    @{B}* Quit@{UB}
      This button quits ThumbNailMaker.
@ENDNODE

@NODE "History" "History"

 @{FG SHINE}@{U}History@{UU}:@{FG TEXT}

   @{B}0.1 - 0.9:@{UB}
   · Internal Betas!

   @{B}1.0:@{UB} @{FG SHINE}(1998-11-08) (18657 bytes)@{FG TEXT}
   · Makes ThumbNails of pictures.
   · Makes HTML file for pictures.
   · Made the GUI.
   · Added the menus.
   · Wrote the Guide.

   @{B}1.1:@{UB} @{FG SHINE}(1998-11-10) (18716 bytes)@{FG TEXT}
   · You can choose where the drawer that contains the pics are.
   · Some small bugfixes/optimizations.

   @{B}1.2:@{UB} @{FG SHINE}(1998-11-25) (22710 bytes)@{FG TEXT}
   · Added the MUI interface.
   · Made a new Save/Use prefs system... (Faster and smaller!)

   @{B}1.3:@{UB} @{FG SHINE}(1998-12-04) (16303 bytes)@{FG TEXT}
   · Fixed the problem with pictures with a space in the name!

   @{B}1.4:@{UB} @{FG SHINE}(1999-06-25) (14855 bytes)@{FG TEXT}
   · I now found the bug that Jonas Davidsson told me about, which caused the
     HTML making procedure to stuck in an endless loop... Fixed it!
   · Corrected some other small mistakes, that didn't effect the program
     really. But they annoyed me! ;)
   · Added a ASL Requester for the GFXCon path!
   · Optimized the program.
   · It won't save the settings in ENVARC: / ENV: anymore!!!

   @{B}1.5:@{UB} @{FG SHINE}(1999-07-03) (14866 bytes)@{FG TEXT}
   · Fixed a bug when images had several dots '.' in their name, it could
     cause pics to have the same thumbnail! (Thanks to Jonas Davidsson for
     the report!)

   @{B}1.6:@{UB} @{FG SHINE}(1999-07-09) (18522 bytes)@{FG TEXT}
   · Added the option to add filename and/or size under the pictures.
     You can also set the size of the filename and size!
   · Moved the General Settings page to the Main.
   · The index files is named index#.html (no t_) and the pics are named
     name_t.ext instead of t_name.ext!
   · When started, the checkmark Picture Page was always on, thanks Jari
     Karjalainen!
   · Added so you can choose a background picture.
   · Added so you can set the colours for: TEXT, LINK, ALINK and VLINK!
   · Moved the BGColor to a separate page, with the above!
   · Added a space between the filename and the size

   @{B}1.7:@{UB} @{FG SHINE}(1999-07-19) (24633 bytes)@{FG TEXT}
   · Moved around everything in the GUI!
   · Added the option to put a linefeed between the pic and text!
   · Added so you can choose where to put the links to the Indexpages!
   · Added so you can choose the size of the Index links!
   · Added a new window that opens when ThumbNailMaker works, and let you
     know what's going on in that window instead of a CON:
     It also has some progressbars so you know how much there is left!
     It will also show you how long everything took to do!
   · Added an abort button to the working window...

   @{B}1.8:@{UB} @{FG SHINE}(1999-08-01) (26358 bytes)@{FG TEXT}
   · Added shortcuts to all buttons in the main window.
   · Rearrenged a little in the GUI.
   · Removed the Base field for the HTML files, use the Header instead, same
     thing!
   · Added so you can choose the names of the HTML files.
   · It will now do a displaybeep when it's finished! (Thanks to Tommy
     Lindgren for making the beep util, in Asm even :) )
   · It will hide the abort button when finished/aborted!
   · When started working, the Start/Quit button will be ghosted. (It will
     crash if you close it with the close button or menu item while it works!
   · Renamed verbose to Quiet and updated help/guide!
   · Fixed a bug when the Source dir didn't end with a slash '/'.
   · Removed the Load Settings menu item, not needed since it loads the
     settings on start!
   · Added so you can set string templates for the HTML Header and Footer (not
     Picture page Header/Footer). The one I have included are: %c=Directory,
     %d=Date and %t=Time.

   @{B}1.9:@{UB} @{FG SHINE}(1999-08-22) (28429 bytes)@{FG TEXT}
   · Fixed the shortcuts, the Source directory and Start had the same shortcuts!
   · Added so you can set string templates for the Picture HTML Header and
     Footer. The one I have included are:
     %c=Filecomment, %d=Date of image, %f=Filename, %s=Filesize, %t=Time of file.
   · Added so it can start a browser (uses openurl.library) and then loads the
     first indexpage into it!
   · Added the string templates: %p=Path and %r=Directory to the Picture HTML
     page (also to HTML page!).
   · The prefsfile is now in a new format! (The old one @{b}DOES'NT@{ub} work!!!)
     But all configs will work from now on!!!
   · Added so %d in Picture HTML pages shows the date of the file, and not the
     current date!
   · Renamed "Press to abort" to "Press to abort, and wait".
   · Added a very nice safetycheck for some fields!
   · Moved some stuff in the GUI (the Main Settings part).
   · Made the JPEG Quality String into a Slider!
   · Fixed the GFXCon path file requester so it doesn't show dirs... (And
     added a Title for the requester!)
   · Fixed the Source Directory file requester so it only shows dirs... (And
     added a Title for the requester!)

   @{B}2.0:@{UB} @{FG SHINE}(1999-09-17) (28819 bytes)@{FG TEXT}
   · Speeded up the Prefs-loading/saving ALOT!
   · Added so the Browser button is ghosted if openurl.library doesn't exist!
   · Added the string templates: %x=X Size and %y=Y Size to the Picture HTML page.
   · Fixed a bug in the Prefs-loading/saving.
   · Fixed the string template Filetime, but it will only work if the file doesn't
     have any spaces in their names. This will be fixed!!!
   · Moved the Picture HTML files gauge below the Index HTML files gauge in the
     progress window.
   · Fixed so it doesn't add spaces between the Previous/Next links if both isn't
     there.
   · Added so you can browse the index pages too, with a Previous and Next links!
   · Fixed so the Thumbnail format is a cyclegadget instead of a string!
   · Replaced the "Stuff under thumbnails" thingies with a string gadget where you
     can add the text under them, with different string templates.
   · Added so you can choose the ThumbNail creation method. Boxfit was the one that
     ThumbNailMaker has always used, Size is new!
   · Forgot to check if the Source directory existed in the Safety-Check... Fixed!
@ENDNODE

@NODE "ToDo" "To Do List"

 @{FG SHINE}@{U}To Do List@{UU}:@{FG TEXT}

