   · @{U}This is on MEDIUM priority!!!!@{UU}:
     · place the keyfile in a different directory :-) have
       the prog check for progdir: and when nothing found check in keys:,
       and so on.
     · Change so it can use other programs than GFXCon to create the ThumbNails!
