       ImageStudio  - David Woolley gave the idea!
       NetPMB       - Matthias Puch gave the idea!
       scalepicture - Matthias Puch gave the idea!
       UltraConv 4??-?Me!
       SView ][     - Me!
     · Add so it can do many dirs at once.
     · Add localesupport. (When more is finished)
     · The popup listing them is read only; it would be nice to be able to
       click on one in that list and have it inserted at the cursor position.
     · Add more safetychecking!!
     · Catch the errors in some more meaningfull requesters? Popping windows
       are not really a nice way for an user to be confronted with a code-hickup.

   · @{U}This is on LOW priority!!!!@{UU}:
     · Fix so TNM says that it needs MUI if that's not started!
     · Errors to come up in a window, like: "kcon:0/0/100/200/TNM errors" or even
       dir:errors.
     · Make so it can store the resulting .html-files in a subdirectory of the
